e cleanup. - **P1-004 (sk-code reference-category entity kind)**: DEFERRED. This is a PRE-EXISTING issue in `.opencode/skill/sk-code/graph-metadata.json:201` that was NOT introduced by packet 070. The strict advisor validator rejects entity kind `reference-category` because it's not in the allow-list. This requires either (a) extending the allow-list or (b) changing the entity kind in sk-code's metadata. Either way, it's out of 070's scope. ## VERIFICATION After all fixes: ```bash # 1. P0 fix verification — no more \"deep-review to deep-review\" patterns in 002/003/004 grep -E \"deep-review to deep-review|deep-research to deep-research\" specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/070-sk-deep-rename/00{2,3,4}*/*.md specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/070-sk-deep-rename/00{2,3,4}*/*.json 2>/dev/null # Expected: zero hits # 2. P1-001 fix — changelog symlinks now point to renamed folders ls -la .opencode/changelog/ | grep -E \"deep-(review|research)\" # Expected: deep-review and deep-research entries; NO sk-deep-* entries readlink .opencode/changelog/deep-review && readlink .opencode/changelog/deep-research # Expected: ../skill/deep-review/changelog and ../skill/deep-research/changelog # 3. P1-002 — skill-graph.json valid + has new signals /usr/bin/python3 -c \" import json d = json.load(open('.opencode/skill/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/skill_advisor/scripts/skill-graph.json')) assert 'iterative review loop' in d['signals']['deep-review'], 'missing positive signal' assert 'iterative review loop' in d.get('anti_signals', {}).get('sk-code-review', []), 'missing anti-signal' print('OK: signals updated') \" # 4. Strict validation bash .opencode/skill/system-spec-kit/scripts/spec/validate.sh specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/070-sk-deep-rename/007-deep-review-remediation --strict bash .opencode/skill/system-spec-kit/scripts/spec/validate.sh specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/070-sk-deep-rename --strict ``` All verifications must pass before declaring DONE. ## OUTPUT ``` PHASE 007 STATUS: <DONE|FAILED> PLANNING ARTIFACTS: <line counts for spec/plan/tasks/checklist/decision-record/impl-summary> P0 FIX: <files modified count + verification grep result> P1-001 FIX: <symlinks fixed yes/no + readlink output> P1-002 FIX: <skill-graph.json updated yes/no + JSON valid yes/no> DEFERRED: P1-003 (family ID, internal grouping); P1-004 (pre-existing sk-code issue) VALIDATION: <child + parent strict exit codes> ``` Begin by reading review-report.md, then plan, then execute B → C → D → E → verification.","recommendation":"sk-code","liveScore":0.865191,"shadowScore":0.7854,"delta":-0.079791,"dominantLane":"explicit_author","timestamp":"2026-05-05T17:05:14.642Z"}
