codex
The stale `sk-deep-*` sweep found the expected command YAML and agent/orchestrator surfaces, plus confirm-mode YAML assets. I’m treating confirm-mode carefully: it is a live workflow surface, not a doc citation, so it needs either explicit inclusion under P1-002 or a sibling finding depending on how narrow the prior packet was.
exec
/bin/zsh -lc "set -e
printf 'TAUTOLOGY_ARROW\\n'
rg -n -e '\\.opencode/(skills|agents|commands)/ ?-> ?\\.opencode/(skills|agents|commands)/' .opencode .codex .claude .gemini --glob '"'!**/z_archive/**'"' --glob '"'!**/playbooks-archived/**'"' --glob '"'!**/review/iterations/**'"' --glob '"'!**/iterations/**'"' || true
printf 'TAUTOLOGY_RENAME\\n'
rg -n -e 'rename "'`?'"\\.opencode/(skills|agents|commands)"'`? to `?'"\\.opencode/(skills|agents|commands)"'`?'"' .opencode .codex .claude .gemini --glob '"'!**/z_archive/**'"' --glob '"'!**/playbooks-archived/**'"' --glob '"'!**/review/iterations/**'"' --glob '"'!**/iterations/**'"' || true
printf 'DIST_FILES_WITH_SINGULAR_ROOT\\n'
