+- `.opencode/skills/deep-review/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:1244`
+- `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:56`
+- `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:56`
